<h3 id="cinget">cin.get</h3>

<blockquote>
  <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cin.get</code>ì€ <u>ê³µë°±</u>ë„ í•˜ë‚˜ì˜ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">char</code> ë¬¸ìë¡œ ì¸ì‹í•˜ì—¬ ì…ë ¥ ë°›ëŠ”ë‹¤.</p>
