<blockquote>
  <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">string</code>ì˜ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">std::getline</code> Vs. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">iostream</code>ì˜ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cin</code>ì˜ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">std::cin.getline</code></p>
